longBusinessSummary: Discovery Harbour Resources Corp., a junior resource company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and evaluation of gold and base metals in Canada and the United States. Its flagship property is the Caldera gold property, which comprise 260 claims covering an area of approximately 3,000 hectares located in Nye County, Nevada. The company is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
